{"tid":2114293,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南華早報一名員工初步確診新冠病毒","createTime":"2020-07-18T16:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T17:07:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90757f5dd2ec96bce31b4d4aed60f40105928050","tid":2114293,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南華早報一名員工初步確診新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n南華早報的內部通告指，一名員工對病毒測試呈陽性，位於銅鑼灣時代廣場的辦公室午夜起會關閉及徹底消毒，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n該名員工最後上班日期是周二，由於在家工作安排仍在實行，當日只有少數員工在辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.SBNCch10LLALFgXVe.uHw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/VIR-SCMP-200718-21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.SBNCch10LLALFgXVe.uHw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FVIR-SCMP-200718-21.jpg&h=2273dc4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d42ad72fe3103570e9a4518bcf683945bcd226e","tid":2114293,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9887e558524d5f3492820a1822f6a71367f11034","tid":2114293,"uid":223664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d42ad72fe3103570e9a4518bcf683945bcd226e","tid":2114293,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:59:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a1780ee279877728cfb787cef48bee39d85bed9","tid":2114293,"uid":131153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0624889b0bf67ac0d404a9d06efd6067db1310c8","tid":2114293,"uid":132488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:03:01.000Z","msg":"吹水啦 我唔信<br />\n如果群組大爆發 我裸跑"},